    ./in.cue:20:23
    ./in.cue:21:13
[incomplete] a.b.c.s: non-concrete value string in operand to +:
    ./in.cue:15:25
    ./in.cue:15:14
    ./in.cue:20:23
    ./in.cue:21:13
a.b.c.s: non-concrete value string in operand to +:
